    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no chips, scratches, or dents of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear and still retaining that new-car smell. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history and no performance issues whatsoever. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
